<F P=106> [From the "Vesti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] INTERFAX reports that a post of Russian border 
guards at the 12th outpost of the Moscow border detachment came 
under mortar fire on Saturday. The fire came from Tajik 
territory. There are no casualties among the Russian border 
guards. 
  Up to 10 groups of militants have accumulated in the rear of 
the 11th and 12th outposts of the Moscow border detachment. The 
command of the Russian border troops in Tajikistan is taking 
urgent measures to repel a possible attack on border detachments 
and military settlements. 

